    box-sizing: border-box;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
&#34;&gt;
    
&lt;h3 style=&#34;color: #4a6fa5; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 22px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;&#34;&gt;📸 展示照片（琳琅）&lt;/h3&gt;
